# Title
`Duolingo (#DUOL) at Current Levels: A Solid Buying Opportunity in Early 2026`

# Date
`2026-01-19`

# Tags
- #Duolingo
- #DUOL
- #Education
- #GPT-5

# Content
```md
As of mid-January 2026, Duolingo (#[DUOL](https://www.google.com/finance/quote/DUOL:NASDAQ)) trades around **$150-155** (near the lower end of its recent range after a sharp correction from 2025 highs above $540), down significantly over the past year. The attached 1-year price % change chart illustrates this steep decline of over **\-57%** from peaks, reflecting market concerns over AI disruption (e.g., GPT-5 demos) and temporary growth headwinds — but this pullback creates a compelling entry point for patient investors.

Here is the 1-year price performance chart for [DUOL](https://www.google.com/finance/quote/DUOL:NASDAQ) (showing the trajectory from early 2025 highs through volatility to current lows in January 2026):

[

